FBIS4-64522 "drweu086_q_94018" FBIS-WEU-94-086 Daily Report 3 May 1994 TURKEY Ankara Security Director Removed From Office Ankara Security Director Removed From Office TA0305130294 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1000 GMT 3 May 94 TA0305130294 Ankara TRT Television Network Turkish BFN [Text] Interior Minister Nahit Mentese has said that Ankara Security Director Orhan Tasar has been removed from office because of the investigation being conducted into the May Day rally. Replying to reporters' questions at parliament, Mentese said: [Begin Mentese recording] An investigation into those incidents is under way. The Ankara security director has been removed from office because of the investigation. [end recording]
